.wordpress.org/_dorsvenabili"><img class="gravatar" src="https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/66591c6fe9d12579cd537b0f1429c011?s=30&amp;d=mm&amp;r=g" alt="" />Rocio Valdivia</a></li>\n<li id="wp-person-bi0xid" class="wp-person"><a class="web" href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/bi0xid"><img class="gravatar" src="https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/e30f51c872aac97f6c8b0bb2c20e0f24?s=30&amp;d=mm&amp;r=g" alt="" />Rafa Poveda</a></li>\n<li id="wp-person-dariobf" class="wp-person"><a class="web" href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/dariobf"><img class="gravatar" src="https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/eafb9a0c553489a272733701b6993ac2?s=30&amp;d=mm&amp;r=g" alt="" />DarioBF</a></li>\n<li id="wp-person-fernandot" class="wp-person"><a class="web" href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/fernandot"><img class="gravatar" src="https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/eb05d8c5ce1b11564c3e948b62afd3e5?s=30&amp;d=mm&amp;r=g" alt="" />Fernando Tellado</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p class="wp-credits-list"><a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/entornogeek">Aída García</a>, <a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/artprojectgroup">Art Project Group</a>, <a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/daniconil">Daniel Melendro</a>, <a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/disespubli">disespubli</a>, <a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/guillegarcia">Guillermo García</a>, <a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/ibonazkoitia">Ibon Azkoitia</a>, <a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/delcastellano">Javier Álvarez</a>, <a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/lchambers">LChambers</a>, <a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/luismontoya">luismontoya</a>, <a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/nilovelez">Nilo Velez</a>, <a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/pablomiralles">Pablo Miralles</a>, <a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/pilarcano">Pilar Cano</a>, <a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/quiqueplegue">quiqueplegue</a>, <a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/egalego">Victor J. Quesada</a>, y <a href="ht